OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter woman stabbed at home
OL,6,FA man has been charged with attempted
OL,7,Fmurder after a woman was stabbed at
OL,8,Fher home in Lancashire.
OL,10,FPolice were called to a property on
OL,11,FWarwick Street in the village of
OL,12,FChurch, Hyndburn at 10:40am on 15
OL,13,FMarch and found a woman in her 30s
OL,14,Fwith a number of stab wounds.
OL,16,FShe was taken to hospital for
OL,17,Ftreatment and is in a serious but
OL,18,Fstable condition.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
