OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter woman stabbed at home
OL,6,FPawel Skros, 39, from Church was
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of attempted
OL,8,Fmurder and has now been charged.
OL,10,FHe has been remanded in custody to
OL,11,Fappear at Preston Crown Court on 15
OL,12,FApril 2026.
OL,14,FPolice are appealing for anyone with
OL,15,Finformation or footage to contact them
OL,16,Fas soon as possible.
OL,18,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,19,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,20,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,21,Four region.
